lead_paragraph: West Indies all-rounder Andre Russell has committed an "anti-doping whereabouts" rule violation, the Jamaica Anti-Doping Commission (JADCO) told Reuters on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: West Indies All-Rounder Russell Commits Doping Violation
